reviewText: Grandkids love Paw Patrol.  Problem is they took it home.  Otherwise a 5 star

Contains these episodes:
Pups and the Ghost Pirate
Pups Fall Festival
Pups and the Pirate Treasure
Pups Save a Train
Pups Save a School Day
Pups Save a Bat
A cute Paw Patrol movie!  My son loves it!
Our 4 year old Granddaughter loves it.
Gift for a friend ... she loves it !
My grandkids can't get enough of paw patrol
